TITLE: Episode 37 - Why Hospital Band-Aids Cost $30
DESCRIPTION: Jessie interviews a fellow registered nurse and friend on what the hell is happening in healthcare. The breakdown from a nurses perspective might be the prescription we all need to get off government.
